name: mind collision
description: such as right and wrong, black and white, both are always in the same container but have different ways and processes from each other. Likewise with our minds, we often face what we hold with our hands, step on our feet, see with our eyes, but at the same time we think of other things, even though we are still with the same body, the same container. That's when the time to enjoy the beauty of the beach and the routine of the office go together
